<div class="container">
  <h2 class= "mt-2">1Gyo diaryとは</h2>
  <h5>忙しくても、1日40文字なら続けられる。<br>
  毎日1行の短い日記を投稿して、昨日の自分からメッセージを受け取ろう。<br>
  気分に合わせた色であなたの感情を表現し、日々の記録をカラフルに彩ります。</h5>
  <div id="carouselExampleFade" class="carousel slide carousel-fade" data-ride="carousel">
    <div class="carousel-inner mt-5">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img src="<%= asset_path '1.png' %>" class="d-block w-100 img-with-border" alt="手順１">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img src="<%= asset_path '2.png' %>" class="d-block w-100 img-with-border" alt="手順２">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img src="<%= asset_path '3.png' %>" class="d-block w-100 img-with-border" alt="手順３">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img src="<%= asset_path '4.png' %>" class="d-block w-100 img-with-border" alt="手順４">
      </div>
    </div>
    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-target="#carouselExampleFade" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </button>
    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-target="#carouselExampleFade" data-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </button>
  </div>
  <div class="row  pt-2 justify-content-center btn-container">
    <%= link_to "新規登録", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-secondary mb-3 sign_in" %>
  </div>
</div>


